$interpreted: Kittyeyes: Your name...is NEKO, right?
Kittyeyes: What are you doing waving your arms around at nothing? You've been doing it for a while now.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: I'm channeling my inner power! Isn't this a world inside a video game?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Therefore, as the MC, NEKO only has to do this! Or this! Huh! HA!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: And flames will come shooting out of my hand! That or I can summon lightning or some kind of divine beast to help me fight...
Kittyeyes: I have absolutely no idea what you're talking about...*sigh*...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Ay! Why do you keep sighing?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Could it be, that you feel that NEKO is responsible for getting you caught?
Kittyeyes: It has nothing to do with you. I'm worried about brother Roger... Although brother Roger is a strong fighter, there's a lot of those bandits.
Kittyeyes: On top of that, if brother Roger's symptoms occur again...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: You've been brother Roger this, brother Roger that all this time. Is he your boyfriend or something?
Kittyeyes: Boyfriend...what's a boyfriend?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: You don't know? Hmm...boyfriend means...lovers! That's right, lovers!
Kittyeyes: Lovers!? W-w-w-what are you talking about!?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Hehe~ NEKO was just taking a shot in the dark. Judging by your reaction, NEKO was right on the money, wasn't I!
Kittyeyes: N-no! That's not the case...I'm not...No, that's not it either...

Kittyeyes: ... Even though I like brother Roger, he merely treats me as his little sister...
So, we're not really l-lovers. Like, not at all...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ......

Kittyeyes: W-why aren't you saying anything now?
Please don't look at me with those pitiful eyes...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: NEKO's not gonna pity you. It's just...I can sort of understand how you feel...like a little, just a little though.
Kittyeyes: Understand how I feel? You...wait.
Kittyeyes: Do you hear something?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...It-It sounded like the roar of some sort of beast? Sounds a bit scary.
Kittyeyes: Why does it sound like brother Roger...!?
Bandit Goon: Hey! You two, behave yourself!
Kittyeyes: Damnit, we have to get out of here! Got to figure out a way to take care of that guard...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: I wonder...if we can use the things inside this prison cell?
